Package com.adobe.xfa

Class Measurement

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.adobe.xfa.Attribute
      • com.adobe.xfa.Measurement
  • public final class Measurement
extends Attribute
    Measurement class. Used for all attributes that are expressed as an ordinate, such as X, Y, H, W, MinX.
